Package com.csaba79coder.bestprotocol.model.representative.entity

Class RepresentativeTranslation

java.lang.Object
com.csaba79coder.bestprotocol.model.base.entity.Identifier
com.csaba79coder.bestprotocol.model.representative.entity.RepresentativeTranslation
@Entity @Embeddable public class RepresentativeTranslation extends Identifier
An entity representing a translation of a Representative object. This entity contains fields for translating the name, secretariat, job title, address, country, note, and secret note of a representative. This entity is annotated with the @Entity annotation, indicating that it is an entity that can be persisted to a database. It is also annotated with the @Table annotation, indicating the name of the database table to which it is mapped. The entity is also annotated with the @Embeddable annotation, which indicates that it can be embedded within another entity. RepresentativeTranslation is embedded within the Representative entity. Identifier provides the id field inherited by this entity. Id is UUID.
